\c 98 Jehovha Mambo noMutongi ngaarumbidzwe 98 1 Imbirai Jehovha rwiyo rutsva; Nokuti akaita zvinhu zvinoshamisa; Chanla chake chorudyi, noruoko rwake rutsvene, zvakamukundisa. 2 Jehovha akazivisa kuponesa kwake; Akaratidza pachena kururama kwake pamberi pavahedheni. 3 Akarangarira ngoni dzake nokutendeka kwake kuimba yaIsiraeri; Migumo yose yapasi yakaona kuponesa kwaMwari wedu. 4 Pururudzai Jehovha, pasi pose; Danidzirai, muimbe nomufaro, imbai nziyo dzokurumbidza. 5 Imbirai Jehovha nziyo dzokurumbidza nembira; Nembira, uye nezwi rokuimba. 6 Nehwamanda, nezwi romumanzi Pururudzai pamberi paMambo, Jehovha. 7 Gungwa ngaritinhire nezvose zviri mukati maro; Nenyika, navanogaramo. 8 Nzizi ngadziuchire; Namakomo ngaaimbc pamwechete nomufaro;	ti 9 Pamberi paJehovha, nokuti anouya kuzotonga pasi, Achatonga nyika zvakarurama, Navanhu nokururama.
